  <chunk id="30e8d03a5cf6907154b5a3d7c7b23cdc96cf1952.c4" text="Our results indicate that Aspergillus PCR in BAL is of particular interest for both the diagnosis and the prognosis of IA. It is likewise an interesting tool for the diagnosis of non-invasive forms.">
